headline: Record-breaking CIIE 2025 Achievements Signal Global Momentum
summary: SHANGHAI, December 18, 2025--The eighth China International Import Expo (CIIE) has concluded with record results, underscoring its growing global influence and China’s commitment to openness. Over six days, the expo welcomed 922,000 visits—an all-time high and an 8.2% increase from last year. Intended one-year purchase deals reached $83.49 billion, up 4.4% year-on-year.
